data.horoscope_data: Money will come and go with ease over the next few months now that Neptune is in Aries and your transformation zone. Whether you’re sharing finances with someone or giving a friend a loan, your money could be tied up with others. While you might receive windfalls, you could also get some unexpected bills.Focus on balancing relationships with independence when Saturn in Pisces sextiles Uranus in Taurus on Friday. The right partner can give you the security and privacy to find yourself. Don’t be afraid to lean on people every once in a while, Virgo.End the week on a romantic note when Venus in Pisces trines Mars in Cancer on Sunday. This is the perfect day to go on a double date with another couple or have your friends play matchmaker. They might know someone wonderful for you. Use this energy to strengthen your bonds with windfalls and have fun!
